sequenceDiagram
  participant AM as Alertmanager
  participant API as alerts.py webhook
  participant DB as PostgreSQL
  participant BG as run_graph_background_saas
  participant G as LangGraph workflow
  participant MCP as MCP tool servers
  participant RED as Redis state/logs

  AM->>API: POST firing alert
  API->>DB: create incident and job
  API->>BG: launch background task
  BG->>RED: set running session state
  BG->>G: start graph with initial state
  G->>MCP: collect evidence and execute actions
  MCP-->>G: tool results and execution outputs
  G->>DB: update incident and job outcomes
  G->>RED: stream live logs and final status
